{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/8.gif?t=1734569361\" /></p><br><strong>NOCTURIA</strong> is a <strong>short but intense first-person horror game</strong> that immerses you in the overwhelming darkness of your own home. You play as a defenseless 4-year-old child who, under the seemingly ordinary circumstance of waking up at night to go to the bathroom, is tormented and cornered by entities with a dark secret that you must unravel as the night progresses.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> First-person short horror story<br></li><li> Lot of <strong>jumpscares</strong><br></li><li> Solve puzzlez in shifting rooms</li></ul><br>Experience terror from the perspective of a vulnerable child, intensifying the feelings of helplessness and fear. The first-person perspective fully immerses you in the nightmare, making every shadow and sound a potential threat.<br><br><strong>Will you be able to survive the night and unveil the dark secrets lurking within your own home?</strong><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/Story.png?t=1734569361\" /></p><br>In the middle of the night, when your parents decide to go out and leave you in the care of your older teenage sister, you find yourself embroiled in a new and terrifying adventure. But this time, it will be much more intense than usual. <strong>It could even be the last one</strong>.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/gameplay.png?t=1734569361\" /></p><br>The game's narrative masterfully combines exploration, chilling events, and increasingly complex puzzle-solving. As you explore different areas of your home plunged into <strong>crushing darkness</strong>, you'll gather clues about the former inhabitants and unravel a terrible mystery, including the fate of one of them... <strong>But be careful, the monster is still loose.</strong><br><br>Pay close attention to every detail and sound; they will be your only guides in the night. Objects and furniture may change places, leaving you trapped and disoriented in your own house. Use the elements you find around you\u2014<strong>they could be your best allies to survive the night and discover that not everything is a product of your imagination.</strong><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/puzzles_y_desafios_blanco.png?t=1734569361\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734569361","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734569361","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/fe5cf5d789034c43e534f63674cd321d68db6e72/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734569361","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/fe5cf5d789034c43e534f63674cd321d68db6e72/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734569361","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/8.gif?t=1734569361\" /></p><br><strong>NOCTURIA</strong> is a <strong>short but intense first-person horror game</strong> that immerses you in the overwhelming darkness of your own home. You play as a defenseless 4-year-old child who, under the seemingly ordinary circumstance of waking up at night to go to the bathroom, is tormented and cornered by entities with a dark secret that you must unravel as the 